{"tid":624854,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[FG RN] 返工返到覺得自己好廢","createTime":"2018-04-11T03:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T02:56:15.000Z","uid":176223,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02cd1b74cd1c2a5ad47740f63d91b3c913bafc05","tid":624854,"uid":176223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"返緊specialty 第8個月<br />\n好多野都唔識 又take up得慢<br />\n返工自己就係最廢果個<br />\n同期果啲都撈得掂過自己<br />\n未至於harm pt 報airs果啲<br />\n甩甩漏漏 好多野都要人提 唔得醒目<br />\n俾人話得又 由本身無自信變到更無自信 <br />\n初初入ward 咩都想學想試 想快啲上手幫到手<br />\n到依家咩新野都唔想試 驚做錯<br />\n有時跟檔柒左 就唔敢再跟果個醫生檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得醫生 senior都睇唔起自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家都唔算地獄ward<br />\n有啲懷疑係自己性格問題 太緊張 結果咩都做唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪應該早quit早享受<br />\n<br />\n有無同路巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2c89ba10e2337cbddec8c134f91795277f0e00","tid":624854,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"我唔係RN 但身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好down"},{"pid":"cd51178214e08901757c3f646d7e5892d99f7ea1","tid":624854,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"呢幾日心情好低落"},{"pid":"d83dddcd13d1e50b2e4aef38c51d795f9dbeff07","tid":624854,"uid":125909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:23:51.000Z","msg":"我唔係做rn都有咁嘅感覺 orz..."},{"pid":"fe5696b30e1748f5758195e96793266312b1847d","tid":624854,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:43:43.000Z","msg":"過到proba唔使extend 都唔係咁差姐"},{"pid":"e8fc9528a0b6c635ded74f20cdda69fabf786294","tid":624854,"uid":40133,"like":0,"dislike":0,